These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, photography, reading, drawing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, horror, epic, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, skateboarding, weightlifting, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter, tram, snowmobile
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
 2. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
 5. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 8. the person watching western movies is between the person driving the scooter and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching epic movies##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
13. the person watching epic movies is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
14. the person who's hobby is photography is the person driving the tram##1
15. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles     | photography   | drawing | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | western   | drama   | epic  |
| Sport         | skateboarding  | weightlifting  | swimming  | biathlon |
| Transport     | skateboard    | tram | scooter     | snowmobile    |

