.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, coffee, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, orange, cherry, lemon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, metal, dubstep, classical
4 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, hamster, mouse
 1. the fan of dubstep is between the owner of the bird and the fan of metal##2
 2. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
 4. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
 5. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the fan of metal##8
 6. the person eating lemon is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 7. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
 8. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of disco is the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
11. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
13. the fan of classical is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
14. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
15. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
17. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
18. the person eating orange is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
19. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | tea | coffee | hot-chocolate  | juice  |
| Food          | lemon     | orange | asparagus | cherry  |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | dubstep  | classical | disco |
| Pet           | hamster | mouse | bird    | hedgehog  |

