.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, writing, reading, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, epic, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, house, d&b, r&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, cricket, lacrosse
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8
 7. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the fan of house##8
12. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | photography    | collecting   | reading | writing |
