.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, asparagus, lime, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, fishing, rock-climbing, baking
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, pilot, accountant, engineer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, baseball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the manager##6
 2. the engineer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 3. the person eating raspberry is the accountant##1
 4. the person eating asparagus is between the manager and the pilot##2
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the engineer##1
10. the pilot is the person who's sport is badminton##1
11. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the right of the person eating peas##8
12. the manager is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the pilot is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
15. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
