 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is not to the right of the colombian##8
 6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person watching superhero movies##8
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
 8. the egyptian is the person watching animation movies##1
 9. the japanese is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8
11. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person watching animation movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
13. the egyptian is not to the right of the person watching animation movies##8
14. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3

