.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, 7up, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  7upcher, fisherman, mechanic, videographer
There are 4 different nationalities: british, russian, german, indian
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, jet-ski, ship
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the videographer##8
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
 4. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the german##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the russian##8
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the indian##6
 8. the fisherman is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
10. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
11. the mechanic is on the right of the 7upcher##1
12. the fisherman is not the british##6
13. the russian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
14. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the right of the fisherman##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | mirinda   | 7up        | lemonade  |
| Job           | videographer     | fisherman | 7upcher | mechanic  |
| Nationality   | british | indian    | german   | russian     |
| Transport     | ship       | snowmobile     | jet-ski    | airplane |

