 3. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the fan of techno##5
 4. the british is not the fan of jazz##6
 5. the fan of indie is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 7. the british is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
 9. the fan of ambient is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the fan of techno##7
10. the fan of ambient is not to the left of the thai##8
11. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
12. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
13. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the fan of indie is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
