.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, mirinda, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, camping, reading, collecting
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, teacher, police-officer, bartender
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, helicopter, roller
 1. the teacher is on the left or right of the bartender##3
 2. the person driving the motorbike is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6
 3. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
 4. the police-officer is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 7. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
 8. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is camping##7
 9. the fisherman is on the far left or far right##3
10. the teacher is not to the left of the teacher##8
11. the fisherman is on the far left##1
12. the bartender is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is reading##1
14. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
15. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
16. the teacher is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4       |
