.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, juice, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, disco, d&b, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, swimming, badminton, rowing
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, tram, ship
 1. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 3. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##8
 9. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
10. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the fan of disco##8
11. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up   | tea     | juice    | cola |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | pop      | d&b     | disco     |
| Sport         | biathlon | badminton  | rowing     | swimming  |
| Transport     | trike     | tram | ship | motorbike     |

