.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, camping, card-games, chess
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, designer, manager, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, superhero, thriller, comedy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, dubstep, punk, electronic
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the left of the paramedic##8
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
 4. the scientist is the person watching comedy movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the manager##6
 6. the person watching zombie movies is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8
 7. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the manager##8
 8. the manager is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 9. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
10. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
11. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the manager and the person who's hobby is chess##2
13. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | chess    | card-games   | dancing   | camping |
| Job           | paramedic | designer    | manager | scientist    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | zombie | superhero     | comedy    |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | punk      | dubstep         | electronic     |

 